## React Prototype Token Map

Use these CSS custom properties in every prototype. Never approximate colors, spacing, or type sizes.

> **Font note:** [PRIMARY FONT NAME] may not be available via CDN. Use `'[FALLBACK FONT]', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif` as the web-safe substitute. Note this substitution in prototype output so stakeholders know the final product uses [PRIMARY FONT NAME].

### Light Mode (default)

```css
:root {
  /* Font */
  --font-family: '[FALLBACK FONT]', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-weight-regular: 400;
  --font-weight-medium: [500 or 600];

  /* Background */
  --bg-primary: [HEX];     /* Screen background */
  --bg-secondary: [HEX];   /* Card background */
  --bg-tertiary: [HEX];    /* Nested surfaces */
  --bg-alt: [HEX];         /* Inverted surfaces */

  /* Text */
  --text-primary: [HEX];
  --text-secondary: [rgba with opacity];
  --text-tertiary: [rgba with opacity];
  --text-disabled: [rgba with opacity];

  /* Semantic */
  --color-accent: [HEX];
  --color-positive: [HEX];
  --color-warning: [HEX];
  --color-negative: [HEX];

  /* Accent backgrounds */
  --bg-accent: [HEX];
  --bg-positive: [HEX];
  --bg-warning: [HEX];
  --bg-negative: [HEX];

  /* Brand primaries */
  --brand-primary: [HEX];
  --brand-secondary: [HEX];
  --brand-tertiary: [HEX];

  /* Borders */
  --border-primary: [rgba];
  --border-accent: [HEX];
  --border-negative: [HEX];
  --border-warning: [HEX];

  /* Elevation */
  --shadow-sm: [value];
  --shadow-md: [value];
  --shadow-lg: [value];

  /* Radii */
  --radius-xs: [px];
  --radius-sm: [px];
  --radius-md: [px];
  --radius-lg: [px];
  --radius-full: 999px;

  /* Spacing (8pt grid) */
  --space-4: 4px;
  --space-8: 8px;
  --space-12: 12px;
  --space-16: 16px;
  --space-20: 20px;
  --space-24: 24px;
  --space-32: 32px;
  --space-40: 40px;
  --space-48: 48px;

  /* Overlay */
  --overlay: rgba(0,0,0,0.60);
}
```

